cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with face sketch synthesis and similarity measures. It may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it involves image processing. Additionally, machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories are possible as the paper proposes a new measure for evaluating FSS algorithms. Finally, the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category is also a possibility as the paper deals with image synthesis and evaluation.
